Technical specifications and implementation details:
- Configuration object: defineConfig({ test: { /* test options */ } }) where options include environment, globals, setupFiles, coverage options, include/exclude patterns, threads, reporters.
- Environments: node, happy-dom, jsdom variants; setupFiles run before tests to configure globals.

